                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d182">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">738.39/286: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in the Dominican Republic</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Norweb</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Ciudad Trujillo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-01-24T13:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 24, 1938—1 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 4:40 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>9. Legation’s despatch 116 [<hi rend="italic">166</hi>], January 19. The Foreign
                    Minister is leaving for Washington by air January 28.</p>
                <p>Repeated to Port-au-Prince.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Norweb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
